{
  "text": "All reactions were performed at room temperature in freshly prepared assay buffer containing 20 mM Tris pH 7.5, 10 mM MgCl 2 , 10 mM KCl, 0.01 % v/v Tween [CITATION_1] , and 1 mM dithiothreitol.",
